  ('dietitian-moex-09768', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-096-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於糖尿病婦女在懷孕時的敘述，何者錯誤？', '["若有肥胖的情形熱量也不應限制，懷孕期體重增加應維持至少12公斤以上", "在懷孕的第二、三期胰島素需要量會增加", "睡前應攝取點心以免清晨時產生酮體", "建議做適度的運動以改善胰島素抗性"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a06c8ec0af96", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "096040", "c": "112", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "096", "exam_name": "096年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫、心理、呼吸治療、營養師、獸醫人員考試暨醫師分試考試第一試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-09769', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-096-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '王先生是一位 type 2 糖尿病患者，現在他想要去爬山（中強度運動）40 分鐘，在運動前他的血糖是 180毫克∕100毫升，你建議他在運動前應如何？', '["不需攝取食物", "攝取一份醣類", "攝取兩份醣類", "攝取三份醣類"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a06c8ec0af96", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "096040", "c": "112", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "096", "exam_name": "096年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫、心理、呼吸治療、營養師、獸醫人員考試暨醫師分試考試第一試", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
